===Noun===
{{en-noun|pl='''[[children]]'''; '''[[childer]]''' (obsolete); '''[[childrens]]''' (nonstandard)}}

# A [[son]] or [[daughter]].
#* ''Her '''child''' is in 1st grade.''
# A [[young]] [[person]], a [[minor]], especially one who has not yet entered into [[puberty]].
#* ''That '''child''' is up to no good.''
# {{context|computing}} Some [[object]] which has a [[subservient]] or [[derivative]] role relative to another object.
#* ''The '''child''' node then stores the actual data of the parent node.''

